{"tid":518513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Mac也有份！Intel CPU被揭漏洞 修補後速度或減慢5%至30%","createTime":"2018-01-03T12:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T12:25:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0880c61ceb109a3e0e761e87c1f6ef5c3edc18e6","tid":518513,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:10:16.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/146291/thumbnail/d6d6cf9d6f87ada543f72d9caa0c9151.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F146291%2Fthumbnail%2Fd6d6cf9d6f87ada543f72d9caa0c9151.jpg&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=050ab41e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/146291/thumbnail/d6d6cf9d6f87ada543f72d9caa0c9151.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\nWindows及Linux正研究修補漏洞，預計在下個月推出系統軟體更新，將核心記憶體資料隔離，但電腦效能有可能因此下降。Windows及Linux系統在修補漏洞後，<span style=\"color: red;\">電腦速度或減慢約5%至30%</span>。基於保安原因，發展商正研究修補保安漏洞，現時未知漏洞細節，最快要到本月底才會有更多資訊。<br />\n<br />\n漏洞亦影響使用Intel處理器的蘋果64-Bit Mac OS電腦，必需透過軟體更新解決，或是購買沒有這設計缺陷的處理器，但未知Mac目前是否正修補漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/146291/Intel-CPU%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E5%AD%98%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB10%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B-%E6%81%90%E7%88%86%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F146291%2FIntel-CPU%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25AD%2598%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB10%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B-%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2cfcb6da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%